OL,3,CSouthport killer 'no1 target' for
OL,4,Creprisal attacks, top prison officer
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FSouthport killer Axel Rudakubana will
OL,8,Fbe "target number one" for reprisal
OL,9,Fattacks from fellow prisoners, the
OL,10,Fnational chairman of the Prison
OL,11,FOfficers' Association has warned.
OL,13,FMark Fairhurst said Rudakubana would
OL,14,Flikely be held in a segregation unit
OL,15,Ffor his own protection.
OL,17,FIt is unclear whether he will remain
OL,18,Fat HMP Belmarsh in south-east London -
OL,19,Fa high-security prison designed to
OL,20,Fhouse the most dangerous offenders -
OL,21,Fwhere he has been held on remand.
