OL,3,CSouthport killer 'no1 target' for
OL,4,Creprisal attacks, top prison officer
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe 18-year-old was sentenced to 52
OL,8,Fyears in prison on Thursday for the
OL,9,Fmurders of Bebe King, six, Elsie Dot
OL,10,FStancombe, seven, and Alice da Silva
OL,11,FAguiar, nine, at a dance class in
OL,12,FSouthport on July 29 last year, as
OL,13,Fwell as the attempted murder of eight
OL,14,Fchildren and two adults.
OL,16,FMr Fairhurst told ITV News he would be
OL,17,F"surprised" if the child killer did
OL,18,Fnot return to Belmarsh "pending
OL,19,Fassessment for a transfer somewhere
OL,20,Felse in the high-security estate".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
