OL,3,CSouthport killer 'no1 target' for
OL,4,Creprisal attacks, top prison officer
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FHe said: "His life will be absolute
OL,8,Fhell. He is target number one. He'll
OL,9,Fbe looking over his shoulders for the
OL,10,Fnext 52 years."
OL,12,FThe Ministry of Justice told ITV News
OL,13,Fit does not disclose the details of
OL,14,Fwhere prisoners are held.
OL,16,FBelmarsh is one of several high-
OL,17,Fsecurity prisons in the UK, alongside
OL,18,FFrankland, Full Sutton, Long Lartin,
OL,19,FManchester, Wakefield, Whitemoor and
OL,20,FWoodhill.
