OL,3,CSouthport killer 'no1 target' for
OL,4,Creprisal attacks, top prison officer
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThese prisons hold some of the most
OL,8,Fnotorious criminals in the UK, many of
OL,9,Fwhom are serving life sentences,
OL,10,Fincluding Urfan Sharif, the father of
OL,11,Fmurdered schoolgirl Sara Sharif.
OL,13,FSharif was sentenced to life in prison
OL,14,Ffor the murder of his 10-year-old
OL,15,Fdaughter in December.
OL,17,FJust weeks after being jailed, Sharif
OL,18,Fwas reportedly ambushed by two inmates
OL,19,Fin a cell at HMP Belmarsh armed with
OL,20,Fthe jagged lid of a tuna tin on New
OL,21,FYear's Day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
