OL,3,CSouthport killer 'no1 target' for
OL,4,Creprisal attacks, top prison officer
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FPolice investigated the alleged
OL,8,Fassault, with reports saying Sharif
OL,9,Fsuffered cuts to his neck and face,
OL,10,Fwhich he was treated for inside the
OL,11,Fprison.
OL,13,FUnlike Sharif, Rudakubana was not
OL,14,Fhanded a whole life sentence, because
OL,15,Fof his age.
OL,17,FHe was under 18, by just a few days,
OL,18,Fat the time of the attack in July last
OL,19,Fyear.
