OL,3,CSouthport killer 'no1 target' for
OL,4,Creprisal attacks, top prison officer
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThough he will likely die behind bars,
OL,8,FSouthport's MP said his punishment was
OL,9,F"not severe enough" and he, along with
OL,10,Fother politicians, has urged the
OL,11,FAttorney General to review this under
OL,12,Fthe unduly lenient sentence scheme.
OL,14,FThe Attorney General confirmed it will
OL,15,Freview Rudakubana's sentence and will
OL,16,Fhave 28 days to consider the case,
OL,17,Fbefore deciding whether to refer it to
OL,18,Fthe Court of Appeal.
