OL,4,Creprisal attacks, top prison officer
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FDowning Street said it shares "the
OL,8,Fpublic disgust at these barbaric
OL,9,Fcrimes" and the desire "for this vile
OL,10,Foffender to never be on our streets
OL,11,Fagain".
OL,13,FHowever, it confirmed that extending
OL,14,Fwhole-life orders is not something it
OL,15,Fis looking at currently.
